Required Libraries/Languages:
 SystemC >= 2.2
 TLM = 2.0 Draft1
 Boost Libraries >= 1.33.1
 Boost.Python >= 1.33.1
 Python >= 2.4
 gccxml >= 0.9.0
 Py++ >= 0.9.5
 pygccxml >= 0.9.5


In order to start the ReSP setup process, type "./setup.py" at the command prompt: this should start the installation wizard
After ReSP is correctly installed, simply type "./startSim" at the command prompt.

For more details on ReSP and on the installation process refer to https://trac.elet.polimi.it/resp/trac.cgi/downloader/download/file/29/ReSP-Overview.pdf
